OL,3,CLandmark decision rules in favour of
OL,4,Cwhistleblower hospital chair
OL,6,FA former hospital chairman who claims
OL,7,Fhe was forced to resign after raising
OL,8,Fconcerns about care has won a landmark
OL,9,Fruling that he should have enjoyed
OL,10,Fprotections as a whistleblower.
OL,12,FDr Maxwell McLean was chair of the
OL,13,FBradford Teaching Hospital NHS
OL,14,FFoundation Trust when he spoke out
OL,15,Fabout issues including major delays in
OL,16,Finvestigating baby deaths.
