OL,3,CLandmark decision rules in favour of
OL,4,Cwhistleblower hospital chair
OL,6,FHe commissioned an independent
OL,7,Finvestigation that corroborated his
OL,8,Fconcerns - but says he was then
OL,9,F"forced to choose between immediate
OL,10,Fresignation or dismissal".
OL,12,FDr McLean pursued a whistleblowing
OL,13,Fclaim, contesting the trust's argument
OL,14,Fthat he was not a worker at the trust
OL,15,Fand was therefore not entitled to
OL,16,Fstaff protections.
