OL,3,CLandmark decision rules in favour of
OL,4,Cwhistleblower hospital chair
OL,6,FA preliminary hearing has now ruled in
OL,7,Fhis favour, meaning he can move to a
OL,8,Ffull employment tribunal. The decision
OL,9,Feffectively sets a precedent for
OL,10,Fmembers of NHS boards.
OL,12,FDr McLean said: "It's so important
OL,13,Fthat boards of NHS trusts feel able to
OL,14,Fspeak up without fear or favour and
OL,15,Fknow that they can be protected.
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G3/7
