OL,3,CLandmark decision rules in favour of
OL,4,Cwhistleblower hospital chair
OL,6,F"We're not trying to point the finger
OL,7,Fat people and pick on people , we're
OL,8,Ftrying to create safe services, and if
OL,9,Fthere's the fear of doing so by
OL,10,Fraising things that are going wrong it
OL,11,Fwill never work."
OL,13,FDr McLean had been trust chair for two
OL,14,Fyears when he raised a range of
OL,15,Fconcerns, including about maternity
OL,16,Fservices.
