OL,3,CLandmark decision rules in favour of
OL,4,Cwhistleblower hospital chair
OL,6,F"I recognised that we were taking far
OL,7,Ftoo long to investigate newborn infant
OL,8,Fdeaths - 14 months rather than 60
OL,9,Fdays, which is the target set by NHS
OL,10,FEngland. How could learning be
OL,11,Fapplied?" he said.
OL,13,F"An independent review found that the
OL,14,FCEO had fallen short of standards
OL,15,Fexpected for the role. And yet within
OL,16,Ftwo weeks of the board receiving that
OL,17,Freport I was punished for standing up
OL,18,Ffor our communities and for maternity
OL,19,Fcare."
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G5/7
