OL,3,CLandmark decision rules in favour of
OL,4,Cwhistleblower hospital chair
OL,6,FHe claims his contract was effectively
OL,7,Fended and that he was penalised for
OL,8,Fcarrying out lawful duties. A full
OL,9,Fhearing will now decide whether he was
OL,10,Funfairly dismissed.
OL,12,FBradford West MP Naz Shah is
OL,13,Fsupporting Dr McLean, saying he had
OL,14,Fbeen the victim of a "witch-hunt".
