OL,3,CLandmark decision rules in favour of
OL,4,Cwhistleblower hospital chair
OL,6,FA spokesperson for Bradford Teaching
OL,7,FHospitals NHS Foundation Trust said Dr
OL,8,FMcLean had "never raised concerns with
OL,9,Fmaternity care or maternity deaths"
OL,10,Fand denied there were cases where
OL,11,Finvestigations into maternity deaths
OL,12,Ftook 14 months.
OL,14,FThey added: "As these matters remain
OL,15,Fsubject to ongoing legal proceedings,
OL,16,Fwe are unable to comment further at
OL,17,Fthis time. We do, however, welcome the
OL,18,Fopportunity to present our position in
OL,19,Ffull at the tribunal."
